spec_data.Name: drupal7-mediawiki_api
spec_data.Description:
This module provides an input filter which allows the conversion of content
marked up using MediaWiki syntax to html for display on your drupal site, by
using the "parse" feature of the MediaWiki API.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 01 Aug 2017 04:25:18 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Provides a MediaWiki syntax to html conversion input filter
